<p>brilliantly, &amp; the country looks very nice with its covering of snow <br/>Old Fritz threw a lot of bombs at the 8th Battalion but no result I believe Last night we were relieved by the 3rd Batt. &amp; they made a proper mess of it, sent a big fatigue party up with the relieving men &amp; you could see nothing but men for miles all making for the trenches in one long string nothing but good fortune saved them from being wiped out, &amp; to make matters worse they brought a fair number of half drunken men with them, &amp; one or two of them kicked up a great stink  an officer threatened to shoot one of them if he did not hold his tongue but he took no notice of him the officer placed him under arrest a pretty sentence he'll get for drunkeness in the firing line is a</p>
